de.larssh.utils.collection

Class Maps.Builder<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.larssh.utils.collection.Maps.Builder<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - type of the maps key
    V - type of the maps value
    Enclosing class:
    Maps

    public static class Maps.Builder<K,V>
extends Object
    Wraps around map to allow its fluent creation and modification.

    Check out Maps.builder() and Maps.builder(Map) for more information.
